file.name: issue_4832.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: ping that return primitive types
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:8082/'
paths:
  /pingBoolean:
    get:
      operationId: pingGetBoolean
      tags: [Ping]
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            'application/json':
              schema:
                type: boolean
  /pingInteger:
    get:
      operationId: pingGetInteger
      tags: [Ping]
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            'application/json':
              schema:
                type: integer
                format: int32
